If I knew I was going to time travel back,

00:14:32.608 --> 00:14:34.199
I would have written down many draws.

00:14:35.575 --> 00:14:37.980
Hey, but I can tell you one thing.

00:14:38.205 --> 00:14:39.773
You have to buy Bitcoin.

00:14:40.135 --> 00:14:42.423
What is Bitcoin?

00:14:43.023 --> 00:14:43.818
Come on,

00:14:43.842 --> 00:14:45.684
when the time comes, just buy it like I do.

00:14:47.186 --> 00:14:48.658
Oh, in the future,

00:14:48.682 --> 00:14:50.463
do you and Nut end up together?

00:14:57.094 --> 00:14:58.448
I can only tell you that

