Because in the final round,

00:54:16.425 --> 00:54:17.825
we have to use a new original song.

00:54:17.938 --> 00:54:18.987
What were you thinking?

00:54:19.011 --> 00:54:20.982
Coming all this way to celebrate a victory.

00:54:21.315 --> 00:54:22.848
Tired.

00:54:22.872 --> 00:54:24.090
But it's worth it, right?

00:54:24.115 --> 00:54:25.297
Of course.

00:54:26.134 --> 00:54:28.071
I used to think that I
wanted to have a band,

00:54:28.531 --> 00:54:30.157
and invite everyone to go camping,

00:54:30.314 --> 00:54:32.034
and eat Mookrata like this for a long time.

00:54:32.176 --> 00:54:33.164
Now that you're here,

00:54:33.194 --> 00:54:34.176
have you gotten more

00:54:34.200 --> 00:54:35.525
inspiration to write songs?

00:54:35.700 --> 00:54:36.530
Hey, you.

